@NCode006 

No, cheating and NTR are similar but different. With cheating, one of the partners VOLUNTARILY engages in sexual acts. With Netori / Netorare, there's no need for that. Someone can literally get raped, but because they were already in a couple, then it constitutes netori or netorare at that point, depending on who the MC is.

So strictly speaking, everywhere where there is cheating, there should be either netori or netorare.
No, cheating and NTR are similar but not the same thing.

